input file is stream of characters

tokenizing - grouping characters into tokens
- gets rid of noise (whitespace, comments)

token - string of characters that has a meaning with current language context


== Jack tokens ==
keywords
	class constructor function method field static var int char
	boolean void true false null this let do if else while return

symbols
	{ } ( ) [ ] . , ; + - * / & | < > = ~

integerConstant
	decimal number in range 0 .. 32767

StringConstant
	" sequence of Unicode characters not including double quote or newline "

identifier
	sequence of letters, digits, underscore not starting with a digit
==========


== tokenizer ==
handles compiler's input
allows advancing input
supplies current token's value and type
==========


next step - parser

